{"tid":1185451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧提及六四事件 中國大使館：對中國的情況，中國老百姓最有發言權","createTime":"2019-06-04T09:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T10:13:05.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c378412d70f88df7586c62a09f0303f21c846d","tid":1185451,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧就六四事件30周年發表聲明，指美國已經對中國的人權進展失去希望，敦促北京政府停止任意拘留，並釋放所有政治犯。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐美大使館發言人批評，美方出於偏見和傲慢，執意以蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）國務卿名義發表涉華聲明，打著所謂人權的幌子粗暴干涉中國內政，攻擊中國制度，詆毀中國內外政策，挑釁中國人民，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則。中方對此強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n大使館稱，對於上世紀80年代末發生的那場政治風波，中國政府和人民早有定論。改革開放40多年來，中國經濟社會快速發展，民主法治建設不斷推進，文化事業日益趨榮，各族人民生活水平顯著提高，「中國人權狀況處於歷史最好時期」。<br />\n<br />\n大使館表示，中國特色社會主義事業是歷史和人民的選擇，已經被證明是符合中國國情、得到全國各族人民擁護的正確道路。中國堅定不移走和平發展道路，堅定不移推進中國和世界人權事業發展，為國際人權治理做出重要貢獻，「這是任何不帶偏見的人都無法否定的事實」。<br />\n<br />\n大使館強調，對中國的情況，中國老百姓最有發言權。中國人民對美好生活的追求，是任何勢力都無法阻擋的。任何人企圖以種種藉口對中國人民頤指氣使、蠻橫霸凌，任何人企圖鼓吹「文明衝突」，對抗時代潮流，都不可能得逞，終將被歷史所淘汰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1015318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1015318&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=85f20764\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1015318&h=fa3a43c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1015318</a>"},{"pid":"d078a2144f8c77d8019e835ae77cc81f8465edbd","tid":1185451,"uid":75969,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:30:11.000Z","msg":"最有發言權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/3Few8XuEwlPTPx7stYRdrA--~A/YXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz01OTE7aD03MzU-/https://img.huffingtonpost.com/asset/5cef6c082400005300855b86.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3Few8XuEwlPTPx7stYRdrA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz01OTE7aD03MzU-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F5cef6c082400005300855b86.jpeg&h=d90b54f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://s.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/3teAG3mipFAtlQChVXq7Wg--~A/YXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz04ODA7aWw9cGxhbmU-/https://img.huffingtonpost.com/asset/5cef6c092500003000dbd357.png.cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3teAG3mipFAtlQChVXq7Wg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz04ODA7aWw9cGxhbmU-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F5cef6c092500003000dbd357.png.cf.jpg&h=5430ecd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/9153797795/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F9153797795%2F0&h=89a6d2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s.newtalk.tw/album/album/1/5cef9c3220ccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Falbum%2F1%2F5cef9c3220ccf.jpg&h=f659edb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190530/d034761f1d6f4683939c968efbfaffe1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190530%2Fd034761f1d6f4683939c968efbfaffe1.png&h=2aed652e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a46f0c8643350d2db7a04738a11cd17bdd6cd190","tid":1185451,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:31:06.000Z","msg":"去冥界發言"},{"pid":"1ffb187544e46e88bd4781c93f7da768af565591","tid":1185451,"uid":244332,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a79c599d02cdd3d419878e60ef531daec1ac3a81","tid":1185451,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"前提係你要畀百姓發言"},{"pid":"bf87e9c97a909f352edf5ee8383298bf48563089","tid":1185451,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"但「中國」老百姓話要消滅美帝喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684ecb03b85c381fc926e4ca5478535d98fa7052","tid":1185451,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"「中國人權狀況處於歷史最好時期」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bc205bd247e92838adbffd5ac38cbc1b8f9f74","tid":1185451,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:37:43.000Z","msg":"你了解中國嗎？你去過中國嗎？你知道中國從一個一窮二白的面貌把六億以上的人擺脫了貧困嗎？你知道中國現在已經成為人均8000美元的世界第二大經濟體嗎？如果我們不能夠很好的保護人權的話，中國能取得這麼大的發展嗎？你知道中國已經把保護人權列入到我們的憲法當中嗎？我要告訴你最了解中國的人權狀況的不是你，而是中國人自己；你沒有發言權，而中國有發言權，所以請你不要再做這種不負責任的提問。中國歡迎一切善意的這種建議，但是我們拒絕任何無端的指責。"},{"pid":"1ca98da10c24e784b1b44947eeb6dd6a630106c8","tid":1185451,"uid":39974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"有發言權 不過係天安門前面死撚哂了"},{"pid":"057d5eff20cc4e296e67039a83bfd5788d36fb02","tid":1185451,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"你睇吓支那狗翻牆係YOUTUBE留言嗰堆, <br />\n<br />\n就知比佢地發言權就係人類災難啦！"}]}